high_descs: Turn to the right and walk towards the kitchen in front of the dishwasher
Pick up the glass cup on the counter next to the toaster
Turn around and face left, walk to the refrigerator
Open the refrigerator and place the cup inside, close door let chill and then remove
Turn around and walk straight then turn left to the back of kitchen corner shelves
Place the glass cup on the second shelf up
anns.task_desc: Put away a glass cup on a shelf

high_descs: Turn around and head to the dishwasher on the right
Grab the wine glass that is on the counter above the dishwasher
Turn right and head to the fridge
Open the fridge and place the glass on the second rack. Close the fridge. Grab the glass out of the fridge. Close the door.
Turn around and head to the brown shelves in the corner of the room
Place the wine glass on the second shelf
anns.task_desc: Putting a wine glass on the brown shelf

high_descs: turn right, walk to the toaster by the sink
grab the wine glasses on the counter
Turn right, walk to the refrigerator
put the glasses in the refrigerator for a while, take it out
turn around, walk across the room to the shelf in the corner
put the glasses on the second shelf
anns.task_desc: cool the wine glasses on the counter in the refrigerator, move it to the shelf

high_descs: Keep making your way right until you are facing the dishwasher
Pick up the glass from the kitchen counter top
Turn to your right and make your way to the fridge
Put the glass in the fridge for a few seconds and then take it out
Make your way backwards and to your left until you are facing brown shelves
Place the glass on to the shelves
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled glass on the shelf

high_descs: Turn around, hang a left at the table, and walk to the white dishwasher across the room.
Pick up the clear glass to the right of the toaster on top of the counter.
Turn around, hang a left at the table, and head to the black fridge.
Place the glass inside the fridge on the second shelf in the middle near the edge, chill it for seven seconds, remove the glass from inside and close the door.
Turn around, hang a left at the white stove, and walk to the wooden shelves across the room just past the windows.
Place the chilled glass on the second wooden shelf on the right side below the salt shakers.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled glass on a wooden shelf.
